{"tid":2258133,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"白羅斯狗持槍無先兆射震撼彈催淚彈 香港記者幾乎硬食","createTime":"2020-10-25T18:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T06:07:52.000Z","uid":246044,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9468507a0b0b59774b15cca86d6f950cb712f66b","tid":2258133,"uid":246044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:59:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/posts/361681571914915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdbchannel.hk%2Fposts%2F361681571914915&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=09ea4857\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/posts/361681571914915</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dbchannel_hkers/status/1320430361000640515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdbchannel_hkers%2Fstatus%2F1320430361000640515&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=e8ae1756\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdbchannel_hkers%2Fstatus%2F1320430361000640515&h=c06c11d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dbchannel_hkers/status/1320430361000640515</a><br />\n<br />\n【加山傳播】白羅斯反政府示威踏入第十二周，周日（25日）又再有上萬白羅斯人走上街頭，抗議政府操控總統選舉及警暴問題等。警方今周明顯不再克制，在遊行警民對峙期間，警方忽然在毫無先兆下，從防線近距離發射至少多發震撼彈和催淚彈，現場頓時不斷冒起極強閃光，警方之後再持槍衝前拘捕多人。<br />\n<br />\n香港的駐白羅斯特派記者當時幾乎被震撼彈命中，據他所指在震撼彈之後，緊接是8到10發橡膠子彈，多人被捕包括至少2名疑似記者。由於現時白羅斯已經取消記者認證，香港記者事發時亦要趕緊逃命，確保珍貴影像能夠保存並向外界發出。<br />\n<br />\n攝/ Alex Chan<br />\n<br />\n#DBC #DBChannel #加山傳播 #國際 #白羅斯<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\nOn 25th October in Belarus, there is a protest again and a serious police-civil conflict happened. Belarus police fired flashbangs and rubberbullets to protesters, after extremely strong flashes police arrested protestors including journalists. Since the Belarus Government cancelled certification of foreign journalists, journalists from HK had to run for release this footage.<br />\n<br />\nPhoto credit/ Alex Chan<br />\n<br />\n#StandWithBelarus<br />\n=================================<br />\n🔹Follow us on Facebook: @dbchannel.hk<br />\n🔹on Instagram: @dbchannel.hk<br />\n🔹on Twitter: @dbchannel_hkers<br />\n=================================<br />\n《加山傳播》雖然只是一介小網媒，但仍決定從有限資源中，撥出部份到白羅斯進行直擊採訪，望能為香港人帶來第一身，最即時的報導。請支持加山傳播贊助計劃！<br />\n東亞銀行戶口：015-515-68-03356-1<br />\n經FPS轉帳：0533398<br />\n<br />\n凡贊助滿1000元或以上，煩請閣下將個人電郵PM至《加山傳播》的Facebook專頁。未來《加山傳播》舉辦任何活動時，您將獲優先預留門票，亦會不時向您寄送電子版新聞摘要。"},{"pid":"4c161c54e4d0696f5b06113e2a280dfa30900863","tid":2258133,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984356d3d3071172dfba30ff5c63051c9d4dd6d5","tid":2258133,"uid":68722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088f56aa86394539dd11cf1e42a2095839bfe7e0","tid":2258133,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f897e1c356e785edbc8da9b264034356acf18889","tid":2258133,"uid":246044,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 派記者去白羅斯"},{"pid":"72fe6d60a28bd032a91f435a42ffd7cc8aa56e24","tid":2258133,"uid":833,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:03:27.000Z","msg":"戰地記者<br />\n<br />\n雖然上年香港果班已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcd3753140b90f91eba1e19c6d76ac408e7e2ee","tid":2258133,"uid":318505,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:04:24.000Z","msg":"不禁諗起 香港五毛：香港人見到開槍淨係識走走走，仲話光復香港"},{"pid":"f3ec5a089dc057d34e9777d59c25f04053f7fb04","tid":2258133,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f897e1c356e785edbc8da9b264034356acf18889","tid":2258133,"uid":246044,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 派記者去白羅斯"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/96275969_232580341491706_3517651895587962880_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=fWggYRvpE14AX8RUL-L&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=1e90fe40934ff02b5f2a0a265936a7d4&amp;oe=5FBAF8AA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F96275969_232580341491706_3517651895587962880_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DfWggYRvpE14AX8RUL-L%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D1e90fe40934ff02b5f2a0a265936a7d4%26oe%3D5FBAF8AA&h=ede310c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d76061307caca904b91c82d0e2a8794ad4638f6","tid":2258133,"uid":310867,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:12:41.000Z","msg":"由於現時白羅斯已經取消記者認證，香港記者事發時亦要趕緊逃命，確保珍貴影像能夠保存並向外界發出。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>任職當地歷史悠久的白羅斯文傳媒Nasha Niva的27歲女記者Natalia Lubnevskaja，兩個月採訪時不幸成為武裝部隊故意攻擊的目標，大腿被橡膠子彈射中，至今尚未完全康復。<br />\n<br />\n在場的10位記者考慮到前一天的和平示威以流血告終，而且<span class=\"red\">互聯網被封鎖下資訊隔絕，他們清楚採訪的風險，故帶備了記者證，並穿有寫上「press/прэса」的藍色反光衣。</span><br />\n<br />\n突然，20至40名身穿綠色軍服、<span class=\"red\">持械的特種部隊橫過馬路迎面衝過來</span>，部隊從後向示威者群眾發射橡膠子彈。各名記者商討後決定撤退，Natalia則一邊後向退，一邊忙於以手機錄影。「<span class=\"red\">突然間我感到腿部傳來一下痛感，初時以為是撞到石頭，之後才發現牛仔褲穿了個洞，流了很多血。」她強調，「軍官只有舉手示意，但沒有發出警告，幾秒後子彈就飛過來，我們根本沒有時間逃走！」</span><br />\n<br />\n醫生指，中彈位置形成直徑2至3厘米的傷口，雖然X光顯示沒有傷及骨頭，但是子彈的衝擊導致傷口附近肌肉壞死收縮，康復需時，而且需等待傷口自然癒合至一定程度，才可接受手術。<span class=\"red\">最終，她在醫院逗留了38天，醫生估計完全康復需要一兩年的時間。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">留院期間，她收到了一位市民傳送給她受傷一刻的片段，顯示軍警從10至12米外瞄準她。</span>她比劃軍警朝她發射子彈，指出自己不是中流彈，而是被軍警故意攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n她親撰一封陳述書，連同受傷片段寄給政府，要求徹查行兇者。正常情況下，官方需時3至10天即完成調查，但這次牽及政治因素，<span class=\"red\">她笑說「等了2個月，連接納都未被接納」。一些政府官員曾兩度到醫院看她，她坦言不知道他們來做甚麼。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201019/2WOR2HZGBJH4NDEOWIV2LJBSQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201019%2F2WOR2HZGBJH4NDEOWIV2LJBSQY%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=18fa242a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201019%2F2WOR2HZGBJH4NDEOWIV2LJBSQY%2F&h=3d557111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201019/2WOR2HZGBJH4NDEOWIV2LJBSQY/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戰地記者買少見少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，Lukashenko由94年連任6屆，做咗成26年，仲向普京靠攏"},{"pid":"b7e25c12665d08c02154749aedd91005a78540d9","tid":2258133,"uid":321026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:22:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e109134538c7dea423427add685fac476ae6640","tid":2258133,"uid":173326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f897e1c356e785edbc8da9b264034356acf18889","tid":2258133,"uid":246044,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 派記者去白羅斯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:22:42.000Z","msg":"白羅斯戰地咁濟，開頭twitter上都有connect香港，而家可能太忙，香港人俾啲關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/VoicesBelarus/status/1320375436652781569?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVoicesBelarus%2Fstatus%2F1320375436652781569%3Fs%3D19&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=8877c25b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVoicesBelarus%2Fstatus%2F1320375436652781569%3Fs%3D19&h=dfa1a92b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/VoicesBelarus/status/1320375436652781569?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"3c2560e63a7a1f03838c2f267dd467e32092bd10","tid":2258133,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:24:11.000Z","msg":"twitter 搜尋#belarus<br />\n幫手connect國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6dc94f66a831c732b88c4fcd0acd740ddf97df","tid":2258133,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:28:51.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3bbfa274d9338e499921afd51914768cc1afc62f","tid":2258133,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:50:48.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af7ecd08c69802d179bf64dd9689caab9e921d1","tid":2258133,"uid":143598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f2293ad20858fd9b090943f0358d7111a2913c","tid":2258133,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T20:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5242ce9d0372759362cb2a030fe8795d1df02ff","tid":2258133,"uid":146791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T20:03:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/VoicesBelarus?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVoicesBelarus%3Fs%3D20&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=cc096e97\" data-auto